              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Diferenta principala consta in componente: Codenames Original foloseste carti cu cuvinte, iar Codenames Pictures foloseste carti cu imagini. Ambele se bazeaza pe acelasi mecanism de joc, dar Pictures stimuleaza mai mult gandirea vizuala si interpretarea imaginilor.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-2">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                merita sa cumpar Codenames Duet daca joc in doi?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Absolut. Codenames Duet este special conceput pentru doi jucatori sau pentru joc cooperativ. Este o varianta excelenta daca vrei o experienta de joc mai intima si mai colaborativa, punand accent pe comunicarea intre parteneri.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-3">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                ce varianta de Codenames e mai buna pentru incepatori?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Pentru incepatori, Codenames Original este cea mai recomandata varianta. Regulile sunt simple, iar cuvintele sunt, in general, comune, permitand o intelegere rapida a mecanismului de joc. Codenames Pictures este, de asemenea, o optiune buna daca grupul prefera imaginile.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-4">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                care sunt cele mai frecvente greseli facute la Codenames?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Cele mai frecvente greseli includ: oferirea unor indicii prea vagi sau prea specifice, nerabdarea si frustrarea cand echipa nu ghiceste, ignorarea cartii de 'asasin' care duce la pierdere instantanee, si oferirea unor indicii prea lungi, care contravin regulilor.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-5">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                unde gasesc jocul Codenames in Romania?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Jocul Codenames poate fi gasit in majoritatea magazinelor online de board games din Romania, precum si in librarii mari sau magazine de jucarii. Preturile sunt, in general, in intervalul 70-90 lei pentru variantele clasice.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-6">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                pot juca Codenames cu copii?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                Varianta Codenames Original si Codenames Pictures sunt potrivite pentru copii peste 8-10 ani, in functie de nivelul lor de intelegere. Varianta Codenames: Deep Undercover contine limbaj si teme pentru adulti si nu este recomandata copiilor.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item" id="faq-7">
              <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                cat dureaza o runda de Codenames?
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
                </svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                O runda de Codenames dureaza, in medie, intre 15 si 20 de minute. Acest timp poate varia in functie de numarul de jucatori, de viteza lor de gandire si de complexitatea indiciilor date.
              </div>
            </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="author-box">
      <div class="author-avatar">{author.charAt(0)}</div>
      <div class="author-info">
        <h4>{author}</h4>
        <p class="author-role">{authorRole}</p>
        <p class="author-bio">{authorBio}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <SimilarArticles
      articles={allArticles}
      currentSlug={slug}
      currentCategory={category}
    />
  </article>

  <Footer />
  <CookieBanner />
</Layout>
